      "originalText": "\u2463 READ BYTES\ncontent = file bytes IN MEMORY  \u2190 pristine source of truth (used for compression)\n+ write temp_path (NamedTemporaryFile, delete=False) = OCR INPUT ONLY",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
