      "text": "\u2464  SEQUENTIAL \u2014 compress a COPY (in asyncio.to_thread) BEFORE OCR \u00b7 OCR reads the ORIGINAL temp file \u00b7 NOT concurrent (PyMuPDF is single-threaded)",
