      "updated": 1718000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u2463 COMPRESSION ONLY (NO OCR)\neligibility gate \u2192 IMAGE /\nSCANNED-PDF compress \u2192 validate \u2192\nfallback\nneeds LOCAL is_native_pdf() (OCR\nclassifier not reachable here)",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "EB4",
      "originalText": "\u2463 COMPRESSION ONLY (NO OCR)\neligibility gate \u2192 IMAGE / SCANNED-PDF compress \u2192 validate \u2192 fallback\nneeds LOCAL is_native_pdf() (OCR classifier not reachable here)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
