      "originalText": "\u2464 PERSIST \u2014 compress BEFORE adapter POST\n\u2192 ERPNext /api/method/upload_file \u2192 Frappe File doctype (never GCS) \u00b7 SAME filename",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
