      "text": "STORAGE REALITY (each file \u2192 ONE store)\n\u2022 Genie OCR \u2192 GCS only  sessions/{sid}/originals/{file}\n\u2022 ERPHome attach \u2192 ERPNext Frappe File only (never GCS)\n\u2022 NOT \u2018ERPNext + GCS\u2019 \u2014 no file lands in both\n\u2022 preview/download = backend proxy stream (no signed URLs)\n\u2022 with no session_id the original is not persisted today",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STORAGE REALITY (each file \u2192 ONE store)\n\u2022 Genie OCR \u2192 GCS only  sessions/{sid}/originals/{file}\n\u2022 ERPHome attach \u2192 ERPNext Frappe File only (never GCS)\n\u2022 NOT \u2018ERPNext + GCS\u2019 \u2014 no file lands in both\n\u2022 preview/download = backend proxy stream (no signed URLs)\n\u2022 with no session_id the original is not persisted today",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
