      "text": "TECH STACK (Python \u2014 all already present)\n\u2022 images \u2192 Pillow\n\u2022 scanned PDF \u2192 PyMuPDF (fitz) + Pillow\n\u2022 native PDF \u2192 PyMuPDF rewrite_images\n\u2022 DOCX/XLSX \u2192 zipfile + Pillow\n(validate: python-docx / openpyxl)\n\u2022 classify \u2192 fitz \u00b7 API \u2192 FastAPI",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TECH STACK (Python \u2014 all already present)\n\u2022 images \u2192 Pillow\n\u2022 scanned PDF \u2192 PyMuPDF (fitz) + Pillow\n\u2022 native PDF \u2192 PyMuPDF rewrite_images\n\u2022 DOCX/XLSX \u2192 zipfile + Pillow\n  (validate: python-docx / openpyxl)\n\u2022 classify \u2192 fitz \u00b7 API \u2192 FastAPI",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
