      "updated": 1718000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SCOPE (implemented)\n\u2022 default: image + scanned PDF\n\u2022 flag native_rebuild_enabled: heavy native\nPDF / DOCX / XLSX \u2192 recompress embedded images\n\u2022 as-is: pure-text PDF / CSV / TXT / others\n\u2022 classifier: is_native_pdf() (50 chars/page)\nshared by OCR + compression",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SCOPE (implemented)\n\u2022 default: image + scanned PDF\n\u2022 flag native_rebuild_enabled: heavy native\n  PDF / DOCX / XLSX \u2192 recompress embedded images\n\u2022 as-is: pure-text PDF / CSV / TXT / others\n\u2022 classifier: is_native_pdf() (50 chars/page)\n  shared by OCR + compression",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
