      "text": "OUT OF SCOPE \u2014 never compressed\n\u2022 master-data import files (XLSX / CSV) during\nBusiness Onboarding\n\u2022 logo / branding upload\n\u2192 separate endpoints + services \u00b7 stored as-is\n\u2022 limits aligned to spec \u00a76.1: 10MB/file \u00b7 30MB & 3 files/session",
