      "updated": 1718000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DOCX / XLSX  (OOXML = ZIP of XML + media)\n\u2022 unzip (zipfile)\n\u2022 recompress ONLY word|xl/media/* images (Pillow)\n\u2022 every XML / text / style byte-identical\n\u2022 repack \u2192 same .docx / .xlsx",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "HN_OOXML",
      "originalText": "DOCX / XLSX  (OOXML = ZIP of XML + media)\n\u2022 unzip (zipfile)\n\u2022 recompress ONLY word|xl/media/* images (Pillow)\n\u2022 every XML / text / style byte-identical\n\u2022 repack \u2192 same .docx / .xlsx",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
